Short Conclusion for Exam

This program loads the Titanic dataset, displays basic dataset information, and visualizes the distribution of passenger fares using a histogram.

Pandas (pd) → Used for handling and analyzing tabular data.
Seaborn (sns) → Statistical visualization library built on Matplotlib.
Matplotlib (plt) → Used for plotting graphs and charts.
sns.load_dataset('titanic') → Loads the Titanic dataset from Seaborn.
