df.dtypes → Shows data types of all columns.
Histogram → Graph used to display frequency distribution of numerical data.
sns.histplot() → Creates histogram for data visualization.
df['fare'] → Selects the Fare column from dataset.
bins=20 → Divides fare values into 20 intervals/groups.
plt.title() → Adds title to graph.
plt.xlabel() → Labels X-axis.
